cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata in this file."
title: "Autonomous Physics Lab"
abstract: >-
  Autonomous Physics Lab is a verification-first scientific engine for
  generating, testing, simulating, falsifying, scoring, and reusing physics
  hypotheses through deterministic code and version-controlled scientific
  memory. It is a hypothesis-testing and benchmarking system, not a source of
  automatic discoveries.
type: software
authors:
